Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從小徑上過來時我就聞到了花香\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could smell the flowers when you came down the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜堂已經空置多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This chapel has stood empty for years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳言說有人躲在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are rumours that someone is hiding there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在躲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信魔法嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you believe in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個巫師對她施了咒語\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An enchanter has cast a spell on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她在睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...that's why she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能叫醒她嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't you wake her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要時間幫她醒過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need time to help wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你幫我攔住外人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to help me keep the people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  太感謝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保護好她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep her safe, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數千年來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For many millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,權威者統治著天堂王國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Authority has ruled in the Kingdom of Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制著一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with absolute control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自詡為創世主  天父  全能的神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He named himself the Creator, the Father, the Almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是一派胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is none of those
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他與我們一樣  只是天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but just an angel like ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個黑暗天使在旁輔佐他的統治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he rules with a dark angel by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為真相而戰  卻被從天堂驅逐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We, who fought for truth, were cast out of the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此后  我們在世界之間穿梭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since then, we have lived between the worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀察  伺機復仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watching and waiting for vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類中間迸發出了希望的火苗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A spark of hope is alive among humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位大膽的領袖在召集勇士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bold leader is rallying warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他雖是凡人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He may be mortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他的野心超越了同類\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but his ambitions transcend his kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一條毒蛇受到了召喚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A serpent has been summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個新夏娃出現了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A new Eve emerges.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的反叛時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The time for a new rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將來臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找一個女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm looking for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中等身高  黑發  棕色的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Medium height, dark hair, brown eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫萊拉  她的精靈叫潘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her name's Lyra. She has a daemon called Pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰  是你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你  幫幫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  加把勁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For goodness' sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行器可能還沒準備好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The craft may not be ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就得怪我們倆了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then that is on the pair of us, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清空思緒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后振蕩器壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've lost the rear oscillator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我們走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不喝藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't drink your medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么能好起來呢  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how will you get better, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你們怎么...  -我們不會傷害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How did you-- - We're not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bene Elim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你們的語言說就是天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Angels, in your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以人形與你見面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We come to you in human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Angels?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是想談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟著我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊薩哈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}AEsahaettr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行器應該是摔爛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think the craft is pretty much done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們要怎么回共和國去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how will we get back to the Republic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們總會有辦法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be able to figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有發現嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前路安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like the path is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮官  我們去救人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, let's go get our man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We secure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-安全 -安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Clear! - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧滾威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ogunwe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一位是奧滾威指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which one of you is Commander Ogunwe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的小朋友是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you, and your little friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阿斯里爾·貝拉克瓦勛爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am Lord Asriel Belacqua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意圖進軍天堂王國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I intend to march upon the Kingdom of Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很希望你可以加入我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I should very much like you to join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說過你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard stories about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛跟教廷宣了戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have just made war with the Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you fight that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聽他要說的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我的朋友并不來自你的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends and I, we are not from your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們對你們的教廷沒什么興趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have little interest in your Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是為你而來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起抵抗權威者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Join with me in my fight against the Authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我們有共同的立場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I know that we stand for the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你有多少手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the number you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你的軍隊  但我需要你做領袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want your army, but I need your leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來  加入最終的勝利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me. Be a part of the final victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來日內瓦  麥克菲爾主教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Geneva, Cardinal MacPhail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭長神父  有請\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭長神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我說說逮捕的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me of this arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在現場發現了這玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We recovered this material from the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被當著眾人背誦出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was recited before an audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人聽得如癡如醉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}many inebriated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后還進行了激烈討論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and followed by feverish discussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和怪誕的思想交流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a grotesque exchange of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰羅姆神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father Jerome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得該怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think should be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應以異端邪說的罪名將作者監禁起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The author must be imprisoned for heresy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海斯特神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father Heyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整棟樓里還藏了數十本這樣的書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were dozens more like it hidden throughout the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有出席者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All attendees imprisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和所有持有作者著作的人都被監禁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as well as anyone found in possession of the author's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-戈梅茲  -戈梅茲神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Gomez. - Father Gomez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是我  你會怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you were in my position, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉體贖罪  當眾進行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Physical atonement... in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被訴持有此書的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For those charged with possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許會選擇鞭刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd choose, perhaps, the whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于作者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the author,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采取能留下更持久傷痕的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something which leaves a little more... lasting damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐懼是饋贈  能讓人長進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fear is a gift. It allows people to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會把我們殺雞儆猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll make examples of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴魯克  我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baruch, we do not have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要那把刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need that knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你們別跟著我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you to stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是怎么穿梭世界的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you cut through worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是由塵埃構成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are made of Dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以穿過空中無形的空間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and can pass through invisible spaces in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是通往其他世界的門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gateways into other worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們看得到  但你看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can see them, but you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴爾塞莫斯和我一直在尋找伊薩哈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Balthamos and I have been searching for AEsahaettr...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一場大戰即將來臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because there is a great war coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有有意識的生靈已經卷入了大戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All conscious beings are engaged in a battle already,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是每個人都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}though not all of us know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的力量每分每秒都在強大起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The enemy's power is growing stronger every minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就持有能讓我們獲勝的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you have the weapon that will enable us to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得跟我們去找阿斯里爾勛爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must come with us to Lord Asriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在召集軍隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gathering an army
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-意圖...  -我知道他是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- with the purpose to-- - I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人跟我說過他  他的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone told me about him. About all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The war,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我要拿著它  跟阿斯里爾并肩作戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how I'm supposed to fight alongside Asriel, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟你們走  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't go with you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找我的朋友  萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm looking for my friend, Lyra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里爾的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asriel's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他不會在乎  但她失蹤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that he cares, but she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要我的幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She needs my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀的重要性遠超乎你的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That knife is more important than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是你不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉才是現在對我最重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra's the most important thing to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要馬上跟我們走  -不然呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You will come with us now-- - Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友的事我很遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry about your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出她對你來說很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see she means a lot to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她遭遇了什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們遭到了襲擊  她被抓走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were attacked. She was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-誰抓了她  -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- By who? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撇下她先走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went ahead without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為她不會有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought she would be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我回來時  她就不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I came back, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管阿斯里爾需要什么  讓他等著吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever Asriel wants, he can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我們會一直跟著你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do realize we're just going to keep following you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你回心轉意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們就繼續跟著我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you can keep following me because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我穿越后  你們都找到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've managed to find me every time I've cut through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀  它吸引塵埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The knife. It attracts Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有人類不具備的感知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have senses that humans do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們能找到我  就能找到萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can find me, you can find Lyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶我去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  我就跟你們去找阿斯里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, I will come with you to Asriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do not have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴魯克  他們要不了多久就會找到我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will not take them long, Baruch. They will find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we will be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴爾塞莫斯  我們沒別的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Balthamos, we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是萊拉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was Lyra's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說它跟刀是一個原理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says it's powered the same way as the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許你可以用它找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you can use it to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是由塵埃驅動的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's powered by Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要點時間  但我們會找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will need a little time, but we will find her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管她在哪個世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whatever world she is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉  我在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰  這是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger, what is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬琪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Machi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  我好想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心肝  看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my sweet. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你長高了15厘米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've grown six inches,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快跟我一般高了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're almost as tall as me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.74,0:24:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸還有工作  我就回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy has work to do. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你女兒真可愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a beautiful little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多久沒見著她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long since you last saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.94,0:24:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十個月零16天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten months and 16 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來沒有可能能離開那監牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had no hope of leaving that cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.74,0:24:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你和你的貓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you and your cat
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑來招募我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}came to recruit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.46,0:24:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.58,0:24:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在考慮你到底是瘋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trying to decide if you're a madman...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.22,0:24:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒希望兩者可以共存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I rather hoped the two could coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里爾徐勛爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Lord Asriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我你的戰爭究竟是針對誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tell me who your war is really against,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.06,0:25:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你想要我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and what you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.54,0:25:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向權威者發起挑戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My fight is with the Authority himself--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說過了  但這不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said that before, but it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.62,0:25:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類不能反抗創世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humankind cannot stand against its Creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.98,0:25:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逼我們在他腳邊下跪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he forces us to kneel at his feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.14,0:25:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他并不是創世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he is not the Creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.86,0:25:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天使  -僅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- An angel? - Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.82,0:25:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how do you know all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.42,0:25:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便這是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...even if it were true?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.86,0:25:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾千年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some millennia ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.46,0:25:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個天使發現了權威者的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}another angel discovered the Authority's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.30,0:25:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個天使  澤法妮婭  現在是我的理事會成員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that angel, Xaphania, sits on my council.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.78,0:25:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧滾威  我在召集各個世界的最強大的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ogunwe, I am gathering the greatest from every world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.94,0:25:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括天堂的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From even the heavens above,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想請你來幫我掀起戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I want you to help me wage my war.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.50,0:26:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該感到受寵若驚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should be flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.38,0:26:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是遠道而來  這就對了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I have come rather a long way, so yes, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.98,0:26:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里爾勛爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord Asriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.86,0:26:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.18,0:26:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬琪是我的最小的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Machi is my youngest daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.46,0:26:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我還有一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have another.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.62,0:26:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教廷早就盯上了我們的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Temple have been targeting our children for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但近年來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in recent years...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們抓走了孩子們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they began taking them away...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.94,0:26:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行訓練\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.42,0:26:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿麗婭是教廷的財產\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aria... is the property of the Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.10,0:26:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她看來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To her...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.90,0:27:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只認權威者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is only the Authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.74,0:27:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所認識的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the girl I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.46,0:27:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.42,0:27:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她仍是我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But she's still my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.30,0:27:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你提出的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand what you offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我還要打自己的仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have my own battles here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.30,0:27:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有義務盡我所能  拯救更多人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And an obligation to save as many sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.78,0:27:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒子和女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and daughters as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以嗎  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.66,0:28:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過這種情況  她的精靈被切割了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen this before. Her daemon has been severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.78,0:28:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她才不是邪魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is not demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.14,0:28:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒那個意思  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not say she was. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.74,0:28:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  請允許我解釋  斯特爾瑪麗婭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, if you'll allow me to explain. Stelmaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.46,0:28:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾瑪麗婭和我是一體的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stelmaria and I are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的精靈  我的靈魂  也可以這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is my daemon. My soul, if you use that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.90,0:28:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿麗婭的精靈原本在她體內\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aria's daemon resided within.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.34,0:28:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們和精靈之間的紐帶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The link that binds us to our daemon
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.42,0:28:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常強大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is immensely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.18,0:28:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦它被切斷  便所剩無幾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when it is severed, well, very little remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.62,0:28:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在奪走我們的靈魂  奧滾威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are taking our souls, Ogunwe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.90,0:28:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也帶走了我們的人性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and with them our humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.98,0:28:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣更好控制我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make us easier to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.78,0:28:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把我們變成這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make us this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.34,0:28:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無人機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.42,0:29:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把馬琪帶回來  所有人進屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get Machi on the ground! Everyone, inside now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.38,0:29:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開火  他們想引我們出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold your fire. They're trying to draw us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.14,0:29:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您找我  庭長神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sent for me, Father President?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.02,0:29:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進  戈梅茲神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in, Father Gomez.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.66,0:29:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來日內瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have come to Geneva
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.34,0:29:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為一件要事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a matter of great significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.38,0:29:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉·帕維爾的真理儀讓我得知了一則預言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fra Pavel's alethiometer has informed me of a prophecy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的  我也相信它是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which, if true, a-- and I believe it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.98,0:30:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么它或能讓我們墮入黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}risks plunging us into a darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是世界前所未見的黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the like of which the world has not experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.54,0:30:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此時此刻  世上有一個女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a girl wandering the earth at this very moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.70,0:30:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是夏娃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she is Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.10,0:30:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所有人的母親  一切罪孽的起源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mother of us all, and the cause of all sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.86,0:30:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理儀說  如果這個孩子被毒蛇誘惑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The instrument says that if this child is tempted by the serpent,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.66,0:30:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很可能會墮落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she will likely fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.22,0:30:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦她墮落  罪孽和塵埃就贏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if she does fall, then sin and Dust will triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這絕不能發生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This cannot happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.02,0:30:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就阻止她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.46,0:30:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.54,0:30:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  我們只能等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, we are at the mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.30,0:30:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理儀和解讀者怎么說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the instrument and its user.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.14,0:30:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉·帕維爾的進展出奇的慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fra Pavel's work is unbearably slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.38,0:30:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他找到這孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he does locate the child...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.46,0:31:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就派兵去把她抓回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will send troops to retrieve her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.54,0:31:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請你  戈梅茲神父  去帶隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I would like you, Father Gomez... to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.18,0:31:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很榮幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.74,0:31:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去見見弗拉·帕維爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could perhaps drop in on Fra Pavel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.94,0:31:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看能不能讓他快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if I can speed him up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.86,0:31:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.58,0:31:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么多人在找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All these men after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.86,0:31:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了  這不會變的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you, it'll never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.26,0:32:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世上有些力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are forces out there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.34,0:32:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本無法理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you can't begin to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.54,0:32:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是別那么看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you wouldn't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.26,0:32:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你不希望我保護她嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you rather I didn't keep her safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在囚禁她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're keeping her prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.18,0:32:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.42,0:32:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Afraid I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.82,0:33:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.26,0:33:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在精靈世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is in the world of the daemons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟一個女人在一起  那女人強行控制著她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's with a woman who is holding her against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.98,0:33:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在一座巖洞屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a house carved into the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.14,0:33:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里位于北海上的一座偏遠島嶼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's on a remote island in the German ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.94,0:33:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要乘船去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will need passage on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.86,0:33:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但萊拉沒受傷嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Lyra's not harmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.50,0:34:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  只是在睡覺和做夢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Just asleep and dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.22,0:34:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟我說說那女人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can you tell me about the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.34,0:34:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的精靈是只金猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her daemon is a golden monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.06,0:34:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是她媽媽  -她媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Her mother. - Her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.50,0:34:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉如果跟她母親在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra's mother's the worst possible person
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.26,0:34:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she could be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.74,0:34:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴爾塞莫斯會帶你去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Balthamos will take you to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.38,0:34:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去找阿斯里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must go to Asriel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.42,0:34:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他你和伊薩哈特的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and tell him about you and AEsahaettr.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.94,0:34:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定這樣安全嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure this is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.90,0:34:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接去找萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go straight to Lyra,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.94,0:34:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們很快就將重聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we will be together again before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.10,0:34:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不記得我答應要陪著這男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not remember agreeing to accompany the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.58,0:34:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟緊威爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay close to Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等孩子們重聚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As soon as the children are reunited,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.30,0:34:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們一起來阿斯里爾的共和國找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will both come to me in Asriel's Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.22,0:35:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭長神父麥克菲爾派我來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President MacPhail sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.42,0:35:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.22,0:35:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快找到了  神父  我保證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am close, Father. I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這任務對你來說是個重擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see this task has weighed heavily on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此壓力  如此重大的責任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pressure. Such great responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.86,0:36:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定讓你頭腦很不清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must muddle the mind terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是解讀的最后部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is this... ...final part of the reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的意義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its... meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.78,0:36:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是搞不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...eludes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是需要更多時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能做我們能做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can only do that of which we are capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.26,0:36:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭長神父建議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President has advised
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.50,0:36:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果讀不出坐標\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that if the coordinates are not forthcoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.26,0:36:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么或許現在需要  重新教育你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then perhaps, the time has come to re-educate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.58,0:36:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.58,0:36:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我能找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I will find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.46,0:36:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.46,0:36:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毫不懷疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no doubt that you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.38,0:37:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉  求你  醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra. Wake up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.18,0:37:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.46,0:37:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.94,0:38:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.06,0:38:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.22,0:38:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑不掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們總得試試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.58,0:38:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在這里  或許會有人看到我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hide here. Maybe someone will see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.54,0:38:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.98,0:39:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.70,0:39:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.42,0:39:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.70,0:39:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.28,0:39:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉  你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總能讓我驚奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never cease to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.58,0:39:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.22,0:40:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你為什么要這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do understand why you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.58,0:40:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣跟我在一起感覺很奇怪吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must be strange being here, like this... with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.58,0:40:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我帶你來這里  不是為了關著你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I haven't brought you here to keep you jailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.58,0:40:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了保護你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done it to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra, darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.22,0:40:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要來抓你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are people coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.22,0:40:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dangerous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.50,0:40:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇氣十足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.10,0:40:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不會相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you won't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.14,0:41:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我這是為了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I... I am doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.42,0:41:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  親愛的  來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, darling, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.54,0:41:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你在一起絕不會安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will never be safe with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.70,0:41:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.78,0:41:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮官  他們去礦山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, they're heading for the mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.10,0:41:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會跟我們拉開四英里距離\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will miss us by four miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.66,0:41:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  我們躲到天黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. We'll stay covered until sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.62,0:41:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力反抗  指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Putting up a good fight, Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.05,0:41:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的戰役太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the battle you're engaged in is too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.50,0:41:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便你贏得了對教廷的戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if you win this fight against the Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.98,0:41:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,權威者只會派來更多仆從替代他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Authority will send more servants in their place
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.46,0:41:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼你再次下跪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to put you back on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.66,0:41:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們每個世界都有  我見識到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are in every world. I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.46,0:42:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總說什么其他世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep talkin' of other worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.26,0:42:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像指望我會相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as if you expect me to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.90,0:42:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒撒謊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.58,0:42:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是眾多世界中的一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is but one world among many.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.94,0:42:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個世界里都在發生一樣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In every single one of them, the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.90,0:42:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子被殘害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Children, mutilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.50,0:42:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科學  學習  被視為罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Science, learning, criminalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.23,0:42:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個文明在天空下瑟瑟發抖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and whole civilizations cowering under the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.34,0:42:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾像你一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was like you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.78,0:42:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的世界  我們的教廷叫教會當局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my world, the Temple, they are called the Magisterium
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.22,0:42:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大半輩子都浪費在跟他們作戰上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I have wasted most of my life fighting them
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.58,0:42:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我發現  他們不過是權威者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until I discovered that they were but one arm
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.38,0:42:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量的一根手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Authority's might,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.86,0:42:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那只野獸有無數手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that beast has countless arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.54,0:42:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一值得你賭上孩子們的性命的戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only fight worth risking your children's lives for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.16,0:42:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在別的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}lies elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.86,0:42:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這地上的共和國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Republic, down here in the good Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.62,0:42:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗他天上的王國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}against his Kingdom up there in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是唯一獲得勝利的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is the only way to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.34,0:42:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們砍掉野獸的頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cut off the head of the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.54,0:42:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的便會分崩離析\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the rest will crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.90,0:42:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.72,0:42:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.82,0:42:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我相信的事太難以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you ask me to believe is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.86,0:42:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不容易接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a lot to take in...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.38,0:43:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我帶你看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so, let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.18,0:43:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.18,0:43:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你就可以自己決定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that way you can decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.62,0:43:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶你去別的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me take you to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.10,0:43:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.58,0:43:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別煩我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just let me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.42,0:44:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會想到辦法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.14,0:44:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為他早該到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just thought he'd be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.10,0:44:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道她是怎么讀的嗎  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you know how she reads it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.46,0:44:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些真理儀的解讀者通常要學習很多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Readers of those instruments have normally studied many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.18,0:44:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  他們也需要書籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even then, they can only understand
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.42,0:44:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-才能進行解讀  -她不是在瞎說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- with the help of books. - She wasn't making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.34,0:44:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許她很會...編\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps she's a very... skilled inventor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.86,0:44:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她會解讀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.82,0:44:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它讓她知道了她根本不可能知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It told her things she could have never known,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.54,0:44:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如我父親在哪  這是她的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like where my father was. It's a part of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.78,0:44:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刀是我的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like the knife's a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.98,0:44:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我們在找的港口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the port we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.10,0:44:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只需要找艘船了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, we just need a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.18,0:45:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是尤雷科·伯爾尼松國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am King Iorek Byrnison.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.90,0:45:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們困住了我的一頭熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've trapped one of my bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.78,0:45:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上放了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Release her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能認識那只熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I know that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.98,0:45:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我可以跟他談談  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can talk to him. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.54,0:45:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是萊拉的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Lyra's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.98,0:45:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.06,0:45:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.22,0:45:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.30,0:45:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.74,0:46:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-讓開  小子  -你得停下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get out of my way, child. - You have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.94,0:46:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里還有無辜者呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are innocent people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.94,0:46:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們抓了一頭我的熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have taken one of my bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.26,0:46:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.98,0:46:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一對一地跟你決斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to fight you. In single combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我贏了  你就放過這些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I win, you leave these people alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.86,0:46:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.20,0:46:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以隨意處置他們和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do whatever you want with them, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.38,0:46:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟我決斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wish to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.10,0:46:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你決斗是可恥的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be shameful to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.14,0:46:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如一只離殼的牡蠣一般脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are as weak as an oyster out of its shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.42,0:46:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們讓決斗公平點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's make it a fair fight, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.98,0:46:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有盔甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have all the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.90,0:46:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.34,0:46:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.74,0:46:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.02,0:46:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就更勢均力敵了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be better matched then, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.02,0:46:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你在做什么嗎  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what you are doing, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.94,0:47:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空鐵  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sky-iron, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.30,0:47:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅不可摧  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impenetrable, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.62,0:47:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.30,0:47:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我還是得不戴盔甲跟你決斗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I have to fight you without armor after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.30,0:47:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打不過那個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot fight that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.10,0:47:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把刀太奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That knife is too strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.86,0:47:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你贏了  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You win, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上放了那頭熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Free that bear, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.18,0:47:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們聽到了  快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You heard the boy. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.58,0:47:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is your name, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.78,0:48:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾·佩里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will Parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.14,0:48:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾·佩里  你在找萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Will Parry, you're looking for Lyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.94,0:48:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟她母親在一起  被她囚禁著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's with her mother, being held against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.42,0:48:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們得去救她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we must go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.38,0:48:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭長神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.22,0:48:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去見了弗拉·帕維爾好幾次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I visited Fra Pavel. Several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.50,0:48:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I helped him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.78,0:48:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}focus his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.06,0:48:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中了精神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.46,0:48:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已判斷出  那孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has since divined that the child
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.50,0:48:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正跟她媽媽在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is with her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.62,0:48:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.50,0:48:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了這個情報\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With this information,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.26,0:48:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信我能找到那女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am confident I can locate the girl myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.26,0:49:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我需要使用沒有得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I will need to use methods that aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.70,0:49:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,官方準許的手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}officially sanctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.86,0:49:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要做什么就去做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must do whatever you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你知道了她們的方位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The second you have their position,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.90,0:49:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去找她們  抓到那孩子和她媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}go to them, get the child, get the mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.02,0:49:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她們直接帶回來找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and bring them directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.46,0:49:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗莎·庫爾特是毒婦  擅長擺弄人心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marisa Coulter is evil, she is persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.30,0:49:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別信任她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.82,0:49:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神父  我成年之后  每一天都在預懺悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, I've done pre-emptive penance every day of my adult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.74,0:49:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會不惜一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will do whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.50,0:49:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她們抓回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is required to get them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.14,0:49:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對權威者的忠心不會白費\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your dedication to the Authority will not go unappreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.02,0:51:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asriel,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.90,0:51:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不是在要我去送死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do hope you're not walking me to my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.94,0:51:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡是謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And death is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.90,0:51:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了  死亡是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're wrong. Death is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.10,0:51:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見識過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.14,0:51:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無數戰爭中見過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than my fair share of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.66,0:51:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮官  權威者不知怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, somehow the Authority
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.46,0:51:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲了塵埃的自然秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has managed to pervert the natural order of Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.02,0:51:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他怎么做到的  但等我查清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how but when I find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.18,0:52:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  死亡就會死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}believe me, death is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.22,0:52:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我聽的夠多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.94,0:52:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.82,0:52:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾瑪利婭  聽我令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stelmaria, on my mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.42,0:52:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I want you to bite down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.06,0:52:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.90,0:52:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三  二  一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.10,0:52:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.66,0:52:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到天堂共和國  指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to the Republic of Heaven, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.70,0:52:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是召集軍隊吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd gather my people if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.58,0:52:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的戰爭要開始了  我們必須贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The real war is coming, and we must win it.

